\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 As a hobby just, oh yes. His works were never really - they were in print but it was just coming out in - periodicals like \{BALNK\}
 and - Gaelic - Gaelic magazines. Yes.
