\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Oh yes, yes, if you wanted just - tell. Yes.
