\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 No, no, no. No. But - children - had nothing to do at all but take your food. You see you just - that's your supper. See
? Go away, play out if you like. That's all.
