\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Yes. Yes. Uh huh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9907513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Was she always an easy person to talk to,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9907513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 She showed affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Of course, yes, yes. Good mother.
