Yes. Yes. The water came in on to Castlebay but not on the - on the - outlying districts. They didn't get it 'til - oh I don't know how many years, about - thirty years or so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9907513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 You say this was because of the people coming for the fishing?
