\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 They - they had their board out in the bay there, sleeping on their boats. The
 fish curers had their own - sheds - timer houses on the stations. You would call them shacks just now but they're - they were quite comfortable.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9907513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Were they down by the water then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Yes, oh yes, the fish - well you can - see - see - the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16457627\charrsid11933423 remn}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 ants of it.
