We were talking about punishment, how parents deal with disobedience and your sister was saying that she doesn't remember your parents smacking you at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 No. No. My mother was never for smacking. And - but - she would give a good hard st
ern lecture, which was worse than her hands. Yes. Yes. I there was any - nothing to be done at all, my father would - hit the boys. Smack the boys. I don't remember any of them being smacked really. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9907513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 That wouldn't be often anyway?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 No. No, but we were lectured a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9907513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 What sort of things did they think were most important in life, in bringing you up? What did they emphasise?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Oh well }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16457627\charrsid11933423 i}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 ndecency, and truth. And truth, yes. Yes. Not a lie. Had to be straight. Straight and honest. Yes, oh honesty, yes. Honesty was very - firm.
