\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9907513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 What kind of person would you think they hoped you'd grow up to be?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 To be a good - woman, to be a good girl
 in every way. And to behave - be - obedient, I had to be that. Anything they'd say - things they had. And of course being brought up as - Roman Catholics, we were - we were - made to - to observe the Sunday, and - the church and church teachings. And of 
course we were taught that in school as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9907513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Supposing a child, one of your brothers, hit you, what did they say you should do then? Hit back or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Oh no, no, wouldn't say that, no. No. They wouldn't say that. But they would scold the one that
 - oh it was just - like - like the children of today, they would go home, wouldn't run back to your mother and cry. Oh there was nothing extraordinary of the - island children, they were just like any other ordinary children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9907513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 When grown ups were talking were you allowed to join in?
