Oh no. Oh no, not to hear the conversation at all. Outside. If it was anything private or - things that - scandal or anything that anybody came in to tell my mother or anything like that, we were shown the door. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9907513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 You were brought up to respect your elders?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Yes. Oh yes.
