Oh, church, that was the main thing, midnight mass - on Christmas Eve. And - you were very much on our turn behaving very well, beforehand, be
fore you were were allowed to go to midnight mass, to stay up for it. But - when you came to the - reasoning age, you were allowed to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9907513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Did they cel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8591140\charrsid11933423 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
