ey were making - that's the day they had the party and it was a children}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8591140\charrsid11933423 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 
s party, and you were - you had your friends in with you or you were into your friend's house. And after the party, you - the - mother would boil - perhaps half a dozen eggs, hard boi
led eggs, and you would take them with you up to the top of that hill Ben Hayworth, and if you were strong enough to walk along with the rest you had to follow suit and - walk up the - the side of Ben Eagle and when they would get to the top, they were ro
lling down the eggs. Roll - rolling down the eggs. And you had - the leaders of the party going up the Castle with you, so that you would eat it at the top of the hill. And - you had the - to roll down the eggs.
