\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9907513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Did you play with children from other houses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Oh yes. Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9907513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Would you play mainly with other girls or boys and girls together?
