\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9907513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Were you taught show respect to some people by curtsying?
