\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 I suppose she did. I - no, I don't - didn't hear much about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9907513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 You didn't hear much about her?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9907513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 She had quite an argument with the people about Vatersay, do you remember that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Oh yes. They - they went over there - took - that island to themselves. You - you know that bit -
