\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Well they got prison, they got - they - sent to prison for going over there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9907513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 They got sent to prison?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Yes. But they came out and had the land after all. Had the land, mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9907513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Did the people here support them for doing that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Oh - oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9907513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 There was nobody here who felt they were wrong to do that?
