No, no. We didn't - I - it didn't - at - when I was - young I didn't know anything about roughness or anything like that. A very good - school but not - not today, I don't find that. No roughness at all. Oh we were a very - good schoolmaster at the time
. Yes. He would hear us say or anything - out of the way he would - notice it at once.
