\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9907513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 That's an English thing too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15810227 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 Ye
s. Yes. Oh, to go - keep - to obey, that's what - what we were - to obey, you know, if she'll ask me to do anything - or to tell me what's right and what's wrong, you have to listen and you have to - to obey. Now you do anything out of the way you'll know
 it. You did - I did - never got a slap or a smack. But - oh she had - did have - telling you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9907513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8853742\charrsid11933423 The owner of this croft was Lady Gordon Cathcart?
